data.description: Welcome home! This charmer is equipped with everything you need. Perfect as a starter home or investment property! Are you looking to downsize? This would be perfect for that, too! Wonderfully maintained and spacious backyard that is already fenced in. HOA maintains front and side yard, so the back is all you need to do! Tall ceilings that make the space feel more open, with primary suite located on the main floor, with amazing window bench w/storage! Lovely sized kitchen that flows well into the living space w/granite countertops and beautiful cabinetry. 2nd floor hosts two bedrooms with full bath. Roof replaced in 2022, with newer HVAC system (2021). Amazing location, minutes from downtown Raleigh, and easy access to nearby towns like Knightdale and Garner! Close to Wake Med main campus and very convenient to I440. Do not let this one slip away!
